==German==

===Noun===
'''Popo''' ''m'' (''genitive singular:'' [[Popos]], ''plural:'' [[Popos]])

# [[bottom]]; [[buttocks]]; [[bum]].

====Usage notes====
Usually the first word for this part of the body children learn (compare [[Pipi]], “wee”), and the preferred (by both children and adults) term for a pre-puberty child’s bum; the terms ''[[Hintern]]'' and ''[[Hinterteil]]'' prevail for a post-puberty person’s bum.

====Synonyms====
#[[Hintern]], [[Hinterteil]], [[Po]]

